<paragraph id="5589BE0800581C80A99F00C60429ECC6" pageId="0" pageNumber="19">
The name reflects the host genus, 
<taxonomicName id="AE7441027A0F946709B53F31370FE554" class="Liliopsida" family="Musaceae" genus="Musa" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Musa" order="Zingiberales" pageId="0" pageNumber="19" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="29BBD427E69A448E07C6B49106D58F14" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="19">Musa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName id="603C6D629876E4F9A9BBAA2640AA14BA" class="Liliopsida" family="Musaceae" genus="Musa" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Zingiberales" pageId="0" pageNumber="19" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Musaceae</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
